This commit adds a helper script in the `package.json` when running `ng add @angular/ssr` or `ng new --ssr` that can be used to spawn the SSR server.

Example of script:
```json
{
    "scripts": {
       "serve:ssr:my-app": "node dist/my-app/server/server.mjs"
    }
}
```

Closes #26315

